---
/* No cambiar aquí nada de los imports */
---

<section id="about" class="about-section">
  <div class="about-content">

    <figure class="photo-frame">
      <img src="/assets/p5.png" alt="Alfonso Navarro" />
    </figure>

    <div class="bio">
      <h2 class="about-title">
        <span class="solid">A</span><span>b</span><span>o</span><span>u</span><span>t</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        Physics graduate (Universidad de Granada) and osteopath with 10+ years
        of clinical practice, including 2 years of intensive acute care
        during COVID-19 (2020–2022).
      </p>
      <p>
        I build AI systems at the intersection of clinical reality and
        machine learning — not as a data scientist theorizing about health,
        but as a clinician who has worked under pressure and understands
        where systems fail.
      </p>
      <p>
        Currently developing <strong>IO</strong>, a local-first autonomous AI agent for
        clinical autonomic monitoring, and working with Outlier/Anthropic
        on AI model evaluation.
      </p>
      <p>
        Open to remote collaboration with clinicians, healthtech teams,
        and research groups working on wearable monitoring, autonomic
        dysfunction, post-infectious fatigue, or AI-assisted clinical
        decision support — regardless of location.
      </p>
    </div>


  </div>
</section>

<!-- Poppins 300; posiblemente ya importado, pero lo dejamos por si acaso -->
<style is:global>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300&display=swap');
</style>

<style>
.about-section {
  padding: 4rem 2rem;
  background-color: var(--astro-background);
}

/* Layout */
.about-content {
  max-width: 960px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 3rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

/* Foto */
.photo-frame {
  width: 120px;
  height: 120px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
}
.photo-frame img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  opacity: 0.2;
  transition: opacity 0.4s ease-in-out;
}
.photo-frame img:hover { opacity: 0.8; }

/* BIO */
.bio { flex: 1; min-width: 280px; }

.about-title {
  font-size: 2.2rem;
  font-weight: 300;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  color: var(--text-color);
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

/* Párrafos */
.bio p { font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
</style>
